In $\triangle PQR$, point $T$ is on side $QR$ such that $QT=6$ and $TR=10$. What is the ratio of the area of $\triangle PQT$ to the area of $\triangle PTR$? [asy]
size(6cm);
pair q = (0, 0); pair t = (6, 0); pair r = (16, 0);
pair p = (4, 8);
draw(p--q--r--cycle--t);
