solution:
Let $a$ and $b$ be real numbers.  If $a \ge b,$ then
\[|a + b| + |a - b| = (a + b) + (a - b) = 2a.\]If $a \le b,$ then
\[|a + b| + |a - b| = (a + b) + (b - a) = 2b.\]In either case, $|a + b| + |a - b| = 2 \max\{a,b\}.$

